<p>Windswept Ridge condominiums are located in the gated community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/windswept-ridge.asp" title="The Currituck Club">The Currituck Club</a> and the owners and their guests have use of the  master association amenities which include a clubhouse, golf course, park, , tennis courts, playground, trolley and the pool of the the master association. The Windswept Ridge association also has it's own pool and tennis court. There are 30 units in two separate buildings with 5 units on 3 different levels. The condos sit on a high ridge which offers some excellent ocean views. </p>
